        "timestamp": "2017-06-20 16:00:53.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nhttp-prompt is a 3rd party open source python module, that's the reason for installing python-pip (note python is installed in base image but not pip for module installation).    http-prompt will be used as the wrapper for the REST CLI using the swagger specification for the Telemetry REST API, at least initially (can be used without swagger for other purposes too).   I actually have been using this way for a while for my own testing.  It provides a nice way to navigate through REST resources in a shell with autocompletion, file system like navigation.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
